properties.name: Michelle Fischbach
properties.biography: Fischbach attended St. Cloud State University, and later earned a law degree from William Mitchell College of Law. She served as the president of the Minnesota State Senate from 2011 to 2012 and 2017 to 2018. During her tenure in the state Senate, she also served as the Chairman of the Senate Higher Education Committee.
